d44cabbd600204cdf6e6181907fc9c3","tid":1133064,"uid":27963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f93c42af679cd880a30e1ec456c1864efe096191","tid":1133064,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:27:33.000Z","msg":"機票貪平買咗Tiblis出入，變相走好多回頭路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGeogria<br />\n1 Tibilis 11am到<br />\n2 Mestia<br />\n3 Mestia<br />\n3 Mestia - Tibilis<br />\n4 Kazabegi day tour<br />\n<br />\nAzerbaijan<br />\n5 Baku<br />\n6 Baku<br />\n7 Sheki<br />\n8 Tiblis<br />\n<br />\nArmenia<br />\n9 Yerevan<br />\n10 Sevan &amp; Dilijan<br />\n11 Garni,&nbsp;Geghard<br />\n12 Yerevan<br />\n13 Tibilis<br />\n14 Tibilis 23xx departure<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以俾吓意見，睇吓可以點以最少嘅時間行回頭路<br />\n落機直接衝去阿塞先留格魯最後又會唔會好啲<br />\n14日太少時間了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時徵求旅伴<br />\n12/5出發28/5返港<br />\n歡迎Telegram查詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://t.me/k567123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fk567123&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=2ec61fe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/k567123</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該各位師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:04:43.000Z","msg":"我而家係亞美尼亞覆你，岩岩玩完熱汽球番緊yerevan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分享下我地經驗睇下幫唔幫到你縮交通時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMestia我地由Tbilisi搭直升機飛去<br />\n時間上會快好多，同埋機上景色靚到痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ticket.vanillasky.ge/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fticket.vanillasky.ge%2F&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=98a0fdd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ticket.vanillasky.ge/</a><br />\n去程揀Natakhtari 回程揀mestia round trip<br />\n佢會有接駁車幫你由tbilisi去natalhtari機場<br />\n唯一風險係如果天氣太差會有可能臨時取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而tbilisi來回yerevan可以試下搭過夜火車 <br />\n會多啲白天時間玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTbilisi去yerevan係單數日子20:20開出<br />\n第二日06:55到yerevan<br />\nYerevan番tbilisi就雙數日子21:30開出<br />\n第二日08:00到tbilisi<br />\n啲床位都算ok訓到覺"},{"pid":"aaa317c605d51a0ec499cec2d0b39d6ed666460e","tid":1133064,"uid":27963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f93c42af679cd880a30e1ec456c1864efe096191","tid":1133064,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:27:33.000Z","msg":"機票貪平買咗Tiblis出入，變相走好多回頭路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGeogria<br />\n1 Tibilis 11am到<br />\n2 Mestia<br />\n3 Mestia<br />\n3 Mestia - Tibilis<br />\n4 Kazabegi day tour<br />\n<br />\nAzerbaijan<br />\n5 Baku<br />\n6 Baku<br />\n7 Sheki<br />\n8 Tiblis<br />\n<br />\nArmenia<br />\n9 Yerevan<br />\n10 Sevan &amp; Dilijan<br />\n11 Garni,&nbsp;Geghard<br />\n12 Yerevan<br />\n13 Tibilis<br />\n14 Tibilis 23xx departure<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以俾吓意見，睇吓可以點以最少嘅時間行回頭路<br />\n落機直接衝去阿塞先留格魯最後又會唔會好啲<br />\n14日太少時間了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時徵求旅伴<br />\n12/5出發28/5返港<br />\n歡迎Telegram查詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://t.me/k567123\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fk567123&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=2ec61fe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/k567123</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該各位師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T06:17:25.000Z","msg":"另外行程方面，有幾樣建議：<br />\n1. 如果你唔係trekking既話，不如住ushguli<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然交通無咁方便，但真係靚到痴線，尤其一朝早！<br />\n又可以騎馬行去shkhara冰川下面，絕對係day trip做唔到<br />\n另外車我地來回ushguli既司機好多野講但好好人<br />\n每個影相靚既地方都停低比我地，我地影左勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以問我拎佢fb<br />\n<br />\n2. 我地9日格魯吉亞 7日亞美尼亞<br />\n真心覺得14日既話，點都要5-6日在亞美尼亞<br />\nTatev, Khor Virap, Noravank真係好撚靚<br />\n同埋以首都計，我同女朋友都鍾意yerevan多啲<br />\n啲人純樸啲好friendly，同埋市中心好有特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 第10 11日去sevan同garni 其實半日都唔洗就來回到<br />\n最好係yerevan join day tour去周邊唔同景點 <br />\n玩多好多地方又唔算好chur<br />\n我地去過oneway tour同埋envoy tour 都不錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 你岩唔岩紅酒？<br />\n岩既一定要去格魯吉亞既kakheti region<br />\n啲紅白酒好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75b81ff6e66f9c161009ef07270074509cf2b6b","tid":1133064,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaa317c605d51a0ec499cec2d0b39d6ed666460e","tid":1133064,"uid":27963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f93c42af679cd880a30e1ec456c1864efe096191","tid":1133064,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T18:27:33.000Z","msg":"機票貪平買咗Tiblis出入，變相走好多回頭路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGeogria<br />\n1 Tibilis 11am到<br />\n2 Mestia<br />\n3 Mestia<br />\n3 Mestia - Tibilis<br />\n4 Kazabegi day tour<br />\n<br />\nAzerbaijan<br />\n5 Baku<br />\n6 Baku<br />\n7 Sheki<br />\n8 Tiblis<br />\n<br />\nArmenia<br />\n9 Yerevan<br />\n10 Sevan &amp; Dilijan<br />\n11 Garni,&nbsp;Geghard<br />\n12 Yerevan<br />\n13 Tibilis<br />\n14 Tibilis 23xx departure<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以俾吓意見，睇吓可以點以最少嘅時間行回頭路<br />\n落機直接衝去阿塞先留格魯最後又會唔會好啲<br />\n14日太少時間了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時徵求旅伴<br />\n12/5出發28/5返港<br />\n歡迎Telegram查詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hk